# GlobeTrotter Travel Planner

## Project Description
A travel planning web application that helps users select countries, cities, and get suggestions for hotels, activities, and foods.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React
- Backend: Node.js, Express
- Database: MySQL (demo data used)

## How to Run Backend
1. Go to backend folder
2. Run `npm install`
3. Run `node server.js`
4. Server runs on http://localhost:5000

## How to Run Frontend
1. Go to frontend folder
2. Run `npm install`
3. Run `npm start`
4. App runs on http://localhost:3000

## API Endpoints
- GET /api/countries
- GET /api/cities/country/:countryId
- GET /api/suggestions/city/:cityId
- GET /api/hotels
- GET /api/foods

## Contributors
- Member 1 – Backend
